{"tid":484820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（平民視后）李佳芯證明左「住公屋」都可活出璀璨","createTime":"2017-11-30T11:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T10:58:13.000Z","uid":41351,"like":968,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"90e6e52f411231f62f496f553e3d48ca6c815403","tid":484820,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"娛樂圈要入行不易要站穩更不易，如果有靠山的確易行好多，起碼要選港姐都易入圍<br />\n<br />\n但對於公屋既女孩、要入娛樂圈可說困難<br />\n有身材的賣色相，出下寫真可能是捷徑，但風險都好大。<br />\n<br />\nAli 成長於基層家庭，自小與家人居住於柴灣一個公共屋邨。她曾就讀伊斯蘭脫維善紀念中學，00年畢業後修讀香港城市大學視覺藝術副學士，畢業後任新假期Modal .<br />\n   完成學業，才追求夢想，而不是好多少女為發明星夢放棄學業，也為自己裝備好才入娛樂圈做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/192156_7e059e082d005a653d30c107610dc3f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F192156_7e059e082d005a653d30c107610dc3f5.jpg&h=c2f88872&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/192159_c2f67962e434f1b92a0fa3c716ab5977.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F192159_c2f67962e434f1b92a0fa3c716ab5977.jpg&h=3db0c1cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吃得苦，走過攀山泄水，到過極地影硬照<br />\n斷練了不怕苦的精神<br />\n<br />\n於2008年加入有線主持體育節目，亦有主持綜藝節目如《空間大改造等》。係細台挨左4年，累積經驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/192458_2f5110e82d9c3d8adae9169f5a5a76f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F192458_2f5110e82d9c3d8adae9169f5a5a76f6.jpg&h=84e1370f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/192502_268673ddab3dee60f193daa1a5524120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F192502_268673ddab3dee60f193daa1a5524120.jpg&h=b1dac601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12年自薦入TVB<br />\n沒有靠山，唯有靠自己努力<br />\n係無線一開始做下d三四線角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/193259_0f2e93beded9401d18e87d3f9ca62c70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F193259_0f2e93beded9401d18e87d3f9ca62c70.jpg&h=df2c205e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/193300_3aec7be98080c237b5a97c6a161531f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F193300_3aec7be98080c237b5a97c6a161531f0.jpg&h=44cd190e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慢慢到主持學是學非，受觀眾歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/193522_c89455044ee3477d013ff9328118b899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F193522_c89455044ee3477d013ff9328118b899.jpg&h=6acc60c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人生，等待機會其實同樣重要<br />\n執二攤成為佢上位既機會<br />\n《律政強人》朱千雪讀書辭演<br />\n令佢有機上女一<br />\n《巨輪2》臭雞令她成名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/194347_678043f613a8587fc054611fcb79c7b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F194347_678043f613a8587fc054611fcb79c7b8.jpg&h=2549a2e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n贏得飛耀進步女演員<br />\n《與諜同謀》楊怡嫁人辭演，令佢再當主角<br />\n經歷令人成長，演技也隨機遇進步<br />\n<br />\n李佳芯最近在熱播劇《踩過界》中飾演性格開放愛蒲的法官；同時間演活清純跟狂野兩種風格令她得觀眾喜愛，贏得新加坡視后<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/194928_b8631cfc57024bade579ba47f217670b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F194928_b8631cfc57024bade579ba47f217670b.jpg&h=34b7a1c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人質疑她年資少，沒有資格<br />\n但其實呢位「公屋妹」既人生閱歷可能比好多演多年戲既花旦豐富，在機遇來前做好準備<br />\n<br />\n視后有許多，但Ali算是最貼近民間果個"},{"pid":"388df50b531213f6464972386a7e36880205928a","tid":484820,"uid":41351,"like":23,"dislike":12,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big